    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This gritty salve can be applied to the skin of a creature to form a thin layer of smooth stone on its body for 20 minutes. During this time, it gains resistance 3 to piercing and slashing damage. Further, the creature gains a +2 item bonus to Impersonate a statue or creature made of stone for 8 hours, or until its body is fully submersed in water.",
